url: 'https://github.com/canslab1/BCAT'
abstract: >-
  A mixed opinion dynamics and innovation diffusion
  simulation model that integrates a bounded confidence-based
  opinion dynamics model with an adoption threshold model to
  explore the "best game no one played" phenomenon. The model
  simulates opinion exchanges and product acceptance behaviors
  across four types of theoretical social networks (regular
  lattice, random, small-world, and scale-free) with 400
  agents. Implementations are provided in both Python 3 and
  NetLogo 4.0.5.
